    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, this car is a total dream\u2014it's been kept in a garage and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. Not a scratch or a smudge anywhere! It drives like a cloud and still has that new-car feel. I\u2019ve babied this thing since day one, and I\u2019m looking for a new owner who will love it just as much. You really have to see it in person to believe how spotless it is! Come take a look!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade 1994 Toyota Supra Turbo in pristine factory configuration. This A80 chassis features the legendary 2JZ-GTE 3.0L twin-turbocharged inline-six, mated to the robust Getrag V160 6-speed manual transmission. The sequential turbocharger system delivers linear power delivery with zero evidence of shaft play or boost leaks. Mechanical integrity is paramount; this unit has passed a comprehensive leak-down test with excellent results and maintains consistent compression across all cylinders. The drivetrain is anchored by a factory Torsen limited-slip differential, with all seals remaining tight and dry. Finished in showroom-quality paint with all original VIN tags intact, this example is mechanically unmolested and represents the pinnacle of Japanese grand touring engineering.",
      "price": 49500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Garage kept. No accidents. Full service records included. Spotless interior and exterior.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
