      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a pinnacle of BMW M-division engineering, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and a factory-spec 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission offers short, tactile throws, channeling power to a flawlessly functioning limited-slip differential. This example boasts a documented service history, including a proactive VANOS overhaul and subframe reinforcement, ensuring the chassis maintains its original torsional rigidity. The exterior retains its factory-applied finish with deep luster, while the interior remains free of bolster wear or pixel degradation. A mechanically synchronized, analog masterpiece for the discerning collector.",
